            <h3 class="font-display text-xl font-bold uppercase tracking-wider text-white group-hover:text-accent-bright transition-colors mb-2">Transfer Conveyors</h3>
            <p class="text-base text-white/60">Right-angle and multi-directional transfers</p>
          </a>
